        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "Once, when the woman went up to her room, her little daughter came up too, and said \"Mother, give me an apple.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8316/279798/8316_279798_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "That vexed the woman, but she said, \"Yes, when he comes from school.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8316/279798/8316_279798_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "Yes, give me an apple.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8316/279798/8316_279798_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "Then she felt that she must speak to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8316/279798/8316_279798_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "\"Come with me,\" said she, and opened the lid; \"pick out an apple for yourself.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000017_000000",
