        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "But he was silent, so she gave him a box on the ear, and the head fell down.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8316/279798/8316_279798_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "\"Margery,\" said her mother, \"what have you done!--but now be quiet, and no one will notice; it cannot be helped now-we will cook him in vinegar.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8316/279798/8316_279798_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "Then the mother took the little boy, and chopped him in pieces, put him into the pot, and cooked him in vinegar.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8316/279798/8316_279798_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "But Margery stood by, and cried and cried, and all her tears fell into the pot, so that the cookery did not want any salt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8316_279798_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8316/279798/8316_279798_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8316",
        "content": "When the father came home, and sat down to dinner, he said, \"Where is my son?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
